ATTRIBUTION

This software is a desktop application fork of the metardu project
(https://github.com/error302/metardu), originally licensed under the MIT
License by error302. The original web application's surveying engine,
coordinate-transformation libraries, importers, exporters, and statutory
document generators have been reused, with minimal modification, as the
"packages/engine" subpackage of this desktop distribution.

The original metardu project's README declared MIT licensing but did not
ship a LICENSE file at the repository root. This LICENSE file is added by
the METARDU Desktop fork to formally grant the same MIT permissions, with
attribution to error302 as the original author of the surveying engine.

Vendored third-party agent-prompt directories (.agents/, .claude/, skills/)
present in the original metardu repository have been REMOVED from this fork
as they are not surveying code and carry their own separate licenses.
